episodes.title: CATHOLICS COME HOME - 2025-01-26 - MOONIE CULT MEMBER BECOMES FAITHFUL CATHOLIC
episodes.description:
Hear the inspiring story of a woman who overcame sexual abuse, her family’s secretive cult involvement, and turbulent childhood, to paint Catholic Icons and com home to the Church.
